00:00:41.965 --> 00:00:44.600 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: They're still talking
about your performance on Coast

00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:45.910 align:middle line:90%
to Coast, my radio show.

00:00:45.910 --> 00:00:48.390 align:middle line:10%
>>BAILEY: Yeah, that was
a great show we did there.

00:00:48.390 --> 00:00:50.840 align:middle line:84%
And in that show,
we talked about AI

00:00:50.840 --> 00:00:54.000 align:middle line:84%
