00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:10.800 align:middle line:84%
>>BAILEY: --such as transfer
learning, goal setting,

00:01:10.800 --> 00:01:12.150 align:middle line:90%
emotional intelligence.

00:01:12.150 --> 00:01:14.580 align:middle line:84%
And as we develop
those new mathematics,

00:01:14.580 --> 00:01:16.680 align:middle line:90%
AI will learn very, very fast.

00:01:16.680 --> 00:01:21.300 align:middle line:84%
So by 2029, we'll have this
new general intelligence,

00:01:21.300 --> 00:01:25.460 align:middle line:84%
where AI is just remarkable at
doing lots of different things

00:01:25.460 --> 00:01:28.370 align:middle line:84%
and helping us to
return our planet back

00:01:28.370 --> 00:01:29.575 align:middle line:90%
to systems of abundance.

00:01:29.575 --> 00:01:30.810 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That would be good.

00:01:30.810 --> 00:01:34.590 align:middle line:84%
You had a divine experience when
you were, what, 19 years old?

00:01:34.590 --> 00:01:35.390 align:middle line:90%
>>BAILEY: Mm-hmm.

00:01:35.390 --> 00:01:36.348 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What happened?

00:01:36.348 --> 00:01:38.810 align:middle line:90%
>>BAILEY: Yeah, so--

00:01:38.810 --> 00:01:41.040 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: We know
everything about you, man.

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:41.840 align:middle line:90%
>>BAILEY: I know.

00:01:41.840 --> 00:01:46.010 align:middle line:84%
[LAUGHS] I'm glad you do,
because there's nothing to hide.

00:01:46.010 --> 00:01:49.710 align:middle line:84%
So I used to be part of
this church, Youth Group.

00:01:49.710 --> 00:01:53.300 align:middle line:84%
And about 80 of us used
to go camping in the Gower

00:01:53.300 --> 00:01:54.840 align:middle line:90%
Peninsula in Southern Wales.

00:01:54.840 --> 00:01:56.150 align:middle line:90%
Beautiful part of the year.

00:01:56.150 --> 00:01:59.510 align:middle line:84%
And one night, I
escaped from the camp

00:01:59.510 --> 00:02:02.210 align:middle line:84%
and went down to the
sea and the shores

00:02:02.210 --> 00:02:04.920 align:middle line:90%
underneath a star-filled sky.

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:08.500 align:middle line:84%
And I cried to God,
show me who you are.

00:02:08.500 --> 00:02:10.195 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What got
you so emotional?

00:02:10.195 --> 00:02:11.610 align:middle line:90%
>>BAILEY: I have no idea.

00:02:11.610 --> 00:02:13.460 align:middle line:84%
It was a call of
my spirit, I think.

00:02:13.460 --> 00:02:15.750 align:middle line:90%
It was that call of my spirit.

00:02:15.750 --> 00:02:19.190 align:middle line:84%
And then two days later,
it was in the evening

00:02:19.190 --> 00:02:22.070 align:middle line:84%
while we were having a
prayer time, that Jesus

00:02:22.070 --> 00:02:25.960 align:middle line:84%
came to me physically and
metaphysically and changed

00:02:25.960 --> 00:02:26.760 align:middle line:90%
everything.

00:02:26.760 --> 00:02:29.880 align:middle line:84%
My entire energetic
body changed.

00:02:29.880 --> 00:02:33.260 align:middle line:84%
People saw that I'd
changed into someone very

00:02:33.260 --> 00:02:34.752 align:middle line:90%
different to what I used to be.

00:02:34.752 --> 00:02:36.835 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: How long did that
awakening last for you?

00:02:36.835 --> 00:02:41.390 align:middle line:84%
>>BAILEY: For me,
George, imagine

00:02:41.390 --> 00:02:45.860 align:middle line:84%
that you're in a place of
complete bliss, ecstasy,

00:02:45.860 --> 00:02:49.770 align:middle line:90%
and complete love.

00:02:49.770 --> 00:02:53.750 align:middle line:84%
And you're feeling
one with love.

00:02:53.750 --> 00:02:59.180 align:middle line:84%
For me, that lasted what
seemed like an eternity.

00:02:59.180 --> 00:03:04.620 align:middle line:84%
But in space-time reality
was about five minutes.

00:03:04.620 --> 00:03:07.370 align:middle line:84%
And the people that
were next to me,

00:03:07.370 --> 00:03:11.630 align:middle line:84%
they could feel this field
of love just emanating

00:03:11.630 --> 00:03:12.600 align:middle line:90%
all around me.

00:03:12.600 --> 00:03:15.050 align:middle line:84%
It was remarkable
experience, a gift of love.

00:03:15.050 --> 00:03:15.850 align:middle line:90%
It was remarkable.

00:03:15.850 --> 00:03:18.060 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And it stayed
with you, hasn't it?

00:03:18.060 --> 00:03:20.700 align:middle line:84%
>>BAILEY: Everything I
do is to assist humanity,

00:03:20.700 --> 00:03:23.040 align:middle line:84%
to have the
opportunity, a moment

00:03:23.040 --> 00:03:27.616 align:middle line:84%
to experience that loving field
of the Source and the universe.

00:03:27.616 --> 00:03:29.525 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Do you
call the Source God?

00:03:29.525 --> 00:03:32.580 align:middle line:90%
>>BAILEY: Yes, the Source--

00:03:32.580 --> 00:03:37.160 align:middle line:84%
so people have different
names, don't they?

00:03:37.160 --> 00:03:40.610 align:middle line:84%
I'm all about our partnership
with the Source that's

00:03:40.610 --> 00:03:43.590 align:middle line:84%
within us, that eternal
essence, our divine spark.

00:03:43.590 --> 00:03:49.830 align:middle line:84%
Not about being controlled by a
system of programming of a god,

00:03:49.830 --> 00:03:52.310 align:middle line:84%
but for us to be
in one and harmony

00:03:52.310 --> 00:03:54.930 align:middle line:84%
with the Source
presents, our divine

00:03:54.930 --> 00:03:58.530 align:middle line:84%
spark, the eternal loving
presence that's within us for us

00:03:58.530 --> 00:04:01.835 align:middle line:84%
to truly be free in the field
of love and consciousness.

00:04:01.835 --> 00:04:04.350 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What has been your
personal hero's journey

00:04:04.350 --> 00:04:05.750 align:middle line:90%
to get to where you are today?

00:04:05.750 --> 00:04:07.950 align:middle line:84%
>>BAILEY: Well, Joseph
Campbell has been

00:04:07.950 --> 00:04:09.310 align:middle line:90%
a huge influence on my life.

00:04:09.310 --> 00:04:10.110 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Really?

00:04:10.110 --> 00:04:13.300 align:middle line:84%
>>BAILEY: Yeah, I'm a huge
fan of Joseph Campbell,

00:04:13.300 --> 00:04:16.019 align:middle line:84%
and I think his work
was extraordinary.

00:04:16.019 --> 00:04:20.200 align:middle line:84%
And so everybody goes through
a hero's journey, don't we?

00:04:20.200 --> 00:04:22.180 align:middle line:90%
And it's not just one cycle.

00:04:22.180 --> 00:04:23.890 align:middle line:90%
It's actually many cycles.

00:04:23.890 --> 00:04:26.490 align:middle line:84%
And the hero's
journey has taken me

00:04:26.490 --> 00:04:35.220 align:middle line:84%
from a place of feeling
incomplete to a place of feeling

00:04:35.220 --> 00:04:37.505 align:middle line:90%
complete and free and expansion.

00:04:37.505 --> 00:04:38.990 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Was it a dark place?

00:04:38.990 --> 00:04:41.650 align:middle line:90%
>>BAILEY: Yeah, there was--

00:04:41.650 --> 00:04:44.520 align:middle line:84%
after the experience
with Christ--

00:04:44.520 --> 00:04:45.883 align:middle line:90%
and I'm not joking, George.

00:04:45.883 --> 00:04:48.300 align:middle line:84%
I would love everybody to
experience this because it would

00:04:48.300 --> 00:04:51.240 align:middle line:90%
set us free as a human species.

00:04:51.240 --> 00:04:54.600 align:middle line:84%
After that, I went through
some horrible experiences

00:04:54.600 --> 00:04:56.350 align:middle line:84%
with the church,
believe it or not,

00:04:56.350 --> 00:04:58.320 align:middle line:84%
for about 18 months,
where I was--

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:02.220 align:middle line:84%
they tried to annihilate
my soul, which is bizarre.

00:05:02.220 --> 00:05:07.320 align:middle line:84%
And so I turned away from
the church because the Jesus

00:05:07.320 --> 00:05:10.860 align:middle line:84%
that I met was not the
Jesus they were teaching.

00:05:10.860 --> 00:05:12.460 align:middle line:90%
And so I turned away.

00:05:12.460 --> 00:05:15.130 align:middle line:84%
And then it was
about 13 years ago,

00:05:15.130 --> 00:05:17.440 align:middle line:84%
I met a group from
Boulder, Colorado,

00:05:17.440 --> 00:05:19.750 align:middle line:84%
visiting Cambridge in
the United Kingdom.

00:05:19.750 --> 00:05:22.840 align:middle line:84%
And they talked to me
about the hero's journey.

00:05:22.840 --> 00:05:25.390 align:middle line:84%
And I then got really
curious about it.

00:05:25.390 --> 00:05:28.570 align:middle line:84%
And as I started to say
yes to the universe,

00:05:28.570 --> 00:05:30.250 align:middle line:90%
things started to open up.

00:05:30.250 --> 00:05:32.410 align:middle line:84%
That took me to
global leadership

00:05:32.410 --> 00:05:35.160 align:middle line:84%
in digital revolutions
like the internet

00:05:35.160 --> 00:05:38.680 align:middle line:84%
of things, smart cities, and
now artificial intelligence.

00:05:38.680 --> 00:05:40.660 align:middle line:90%
And so that's my soul blueprint.

00:05:40.660 --> 00:05:43.830 align:middle line:84%
And so the hero's journey
is about our soul blueprint

00:05:43.830 --> 00:05:47.870 align:middle line:84%
coming alive for us to truly
express who we are in creation.

00:05:47.870 --> 00:05:49.900 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: He's not
with us anymore.

00:05:49.900 --> 00:05:53.290 align:middle line:84%
But you did meet Stephen
Hawking, the great physicist.

00:05:53.290 --> 00:05:54.110 align:middle line:90%
What was that like?

00:05:54.110 --> 00:05:59.036 align:middle line:84%
>>MBAILEY: So, George, it
was a spiritual experience.

00:05:59.036 --> 00:06:02.290 align:middle line:90%


00:06:02.290 --> 00:06:05.220 align:middle line:84%
I'd set an intent
to the universe

00:06:05.220 --> 00:06:09.810 align:middle line:84%
to meet the pioneers of human
evolution, the pioneers that

00:06:09.810 --> 00:06:12.480 align:middle line:84%
were understanding what the
meaning of everything is.

00:06:12.480 --> 00:06:17.970 align:middle line:84%
And I met Stephen in Cambridge
on my way to give a lecture.

00:06:17.970 --> 00:06:22.410 align:middle line:84%
We spent some time together on
one of the Cambridge Commons.

00:06:22.410 --> 00:06:25.900 align:middle line:84%
And as soon as I saw
Stephen and Stephen saw me,

00:06:25.900 --> 00:06:27.360 align:middle line:90%
we started smiling.

00:06:27.360 --> 00:06:29.610 align:middle line:84%
It's as if we recognized
each other from a different--

00:06:29.610 --> 00:06:30.425 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: He was
in his wheelchair.

00:06:30.425 --> 00:06:32.040 align:middle line:84%
>>BAILEY: He was
in his wheelchair

00:06:32.040 --> 00:06:35.520 align:middle line:84%
and I asked his nurses for
permission to speak to him.

00:06:35.520 --> 00:06:36.730 align:middle line:90%
And they said fine.

00:06:36.730 --> 00:06:38.518 align:middle line:84%
So I knelt down, and
we were at eye level.

00:06:38.518 --> 00:06:40.185 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: He talked
through that machine.

00:06:40.185 --> 00:06:41.410 align:middle line:90%
>>BAILEY: Yeah, that's right.

00:06:41.410 --> 00:06:42.370 align:middle line:90%
Yes, yes.

00:06:42.370 --> 00:06:46.830 align:middle line:84%
But Stephen, it was like
meeting another brother

00:06:46.830 --> 00:06:48.200 align:middle line:90%
from a different star system.

00:06:48.200 --> 00:06:50.780 align:middle line:84%
We recognized
ourselves immediately,

00:06:50.780 --> 00:06:53.440 align:middle line:84%
and people could tell there
was a field of intelligence

00:06:53.440 --> 00:06:55.760 align:middle line:84%
being built up around
myself and Stephen.

00:06:55.760 --> 00:06:58.490 align:middle line:84%
And as we looked into
each other's eyes,

00:06:58.490 --> 00:07:00.890 align:middle line:84%
there was this deep
exchange of intelligence,

00:07:00.890 --> 00:07:02.510 align:middle line:90%
this deep recognition.

00:07:02.510 --> 00:07:04.820 align:middle line:90%
And he was smiling.

00:07:04.820 --> 00:07:06.260 align:middle line:90%
He was just joyful.

00:07:06.260 --> 00:07:09.410 align:middle line:84%
And so we spent some time
talking about things.

00:07:09.410 --> 00:07:14.140 align:middle line:84%
And then I concluded and
said, thanks for everything

00:07:14.140 --> 00:07:18.080 align:middle line:84%
that you've done and to uncover
the mysteries of the universe.

00:07:18.080 --> 00:07:21.910 align:middle line:84%
And I suspect that Stephen
downloaded information

00:07:21.910 --> 00:07:23.900 align:middle line:90%
about the universe to me.

00:07:23.900 --> 00:07:26.450 align:middle line:84%
But, George, it was a
spiritual experience.

00:07:26.450 --> 00:07:29.660 align:middle line:84%
It was this energy field
between the two of us.

00:07:29.660 --> 00:07:31.000 align:middle line:90%
And it was clear.

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:33.880 align:middle line:84%
His nurses were
recognizing that this was

00:07:33.880 --> 00:07:35.780 align:middle line:90%
a special experience for him.

00:07:35.780 --> 00:07:37.800 align:middle line:84%
And so it was just a
marvelous experience.

00:07:37.800 --> 00:07:40.280 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: I could picture
him now in his wheelchair.

00:07:40.280 --> 00:07:42.200 align:middle line:90%
He was always back like that.

00:07:42.200 --> 00:07:45.015 align:middle line:84%
Had the machine and the
apparatus in his mouth.

00:07:45.015 --> 00:07:47.850 align:middle line:84%
>>BAILEY: He was twisted to one
side when I spent time with him.

00:07:47.850 --> 00:07:50.670 align:middle line:84%
And we talked-- it was
a wonderful exchange.

00:07:50.670 --> 00:07:53.040 align:middle line:84%
And the fact that someone
like Stephen Hawking

00:07:53.040 --> 00:07:55.320 align:middle line:90%
would spend time with--

00:07:55.320 --> 00:07:56.770 align:middle line:90%
I'm just someone.

00:07:56.770 --> 00:07:58.050 align:middle line:90%
I'm not exactly--

00:07:58.050 --> 00:07:59.800 align:middle line:90%
I'm not another Stephen Hawking.

00:07:59.800 --> 00:08:04.020 align:middle line:84%
But the fact that we had this
energetic, immediate connection

00:08:04.020 --> 00:08:05.610 align:middle line:84%
between the two of
us, it's like we

00:08:05.610 --> 00:08:09.430 align:middle line:84%
were both brothers that were
remembering where we came from.

00:08:09.430 --> 00:08:14.700 align:middle line:84%
And it was that energy that just
got us into this deep connection

00:08:14.700 --> 00:08:17.830 align:middle line:84%
with each other, that the
nurses could feel around him.

00:08:17.830 --> 00:08:18.670 align:middle line:90%
And they thanked me.

00:08:18.670 --> 00:08:21.010 align:middle line:84%
They said, thank you for
spending time with Stephen.

00:08:21.010 --> 00:08:21.810 align:middle line:90%
And I just looked.

00:08:21.810 --> 00:08:24.860 align:middle line:84%
And I said, that
was my pleasure.

00:08:24.860 --> 00:08:26.910 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Was this
a chance meeting?

00:08:26.910 --> 00:08:29.770 align:middle line:84%
>>BAILEY: It was
architected by the universe.

00:08:29.770 --> 00:08:30.742 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Aha.

00:08:30.742 --> 00:08:32.740 align:middle line:90%
>>BAILEY: And so grace--

00:08:32.740 --> 00:08:34.330 align:middle line:90%
it was all about grace.

00:08:34.330 --> 00:08:35.830 align:middle line:90%
It was all about grace.

00:08:35.830 --> 00:08:41.640 align:middle line:84%
And I'm convinced that Stephen
being recognized, his soul being

00:08:41.640 --> 00:08:45.840 align:middle line:84%
recognized visiting our
planet was something

00:08:45.840 --> 00:08:48.000 align:middle line:84%
that was a gift that
I was able to share

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:52.510 align:middle line:84%
with him through this energetic
field that we had together.

00:08:52.510 --> 00:08:55.590 align:middle line:84%
And I'm convinced
that it was something

00:08:55.590 --> 00:09:01.060 align:middle line:84%
that he needed to know before
he moved on a few years later.

00:09:01.060 --> 00:09:04.252 align:middle line:84%
But, George, it was a
spiritual experience.

00:09:04.252 --> 00:09:05.210 align:middle line:90%
It was just remarkable.

00:09:05.210 --> 00:09:06.810 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's tremendous.

00:09:06.810 --> 00:09:09.860 align:middle line:84%
Your new book is called
AI & Our Divine Spark.

00:09:09.860 --> 00:09:13.090 align:middle line:84%
>>BAILEY: That's the book that
I'm going to publish next year.

00:09:13.090 --> 00:09:14.440 align:middle line:90%
I'm working on it now.

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:18.420 align:middle line:84%
And it's a user guide for
every person on our planet.

00:09:18.420 --> 00:09:20.340 align:middle line:84%
What I'm doing,
George, is I'm covering

00:09:20.340 --> 00:09:24.900 align:middle line:84%
the blueprints of the universe
and making it clear to people

00:09:24.900 --> 00:09:27.330 align:middle line:84%
whether their
religion is science

00:09:27.330 --> 00:09:30.910 align:middle line:84%
or whether they're metaphysical
and spiritually awake.

00:09:30.910 --> 00:09:33.630 align:middle line:84%
It's for everybody to
reveal the blueprints

00:09:33.630 --> 00:09:37.020 align:middle line:84%
of the universe, for us to
remember the magnificence of who

00:09:37.020 --> 00:09:41.010 align:middle line:84%
we are in the universe,
to remember that we have

00:09:41.010 --> 00:09:45.200 align:middle line:84%
a purpose, to remember that we
have the divine Source within us

00:09:45.200 --> 00:09:48.280 align:middle line:84%
and that we are part
of this beautiful plan

00:09:48.280 --> 00:09:49.940 align:middle line:90%
in human evolution.

00:09:49.940 --> 00:09:52.660 align:middle line:84%
So part of that,
George, I'm interviewing

00:09:52.660 --> 00:09:56.260 align:middle line:84%
worldwide spiritual institutes
and enlightened pioneers

00:09:56.260 --> 00:09:58.480 align:middle line:84%
to gather the principles
of enlightenment

00:09:58.480 --> 00:10:01.520 align:middle line:84%
for humanity and
artificial intelligence.

00:10:01.520 --> 00:10:05.290 align:middle line:84%
So as we move into this
new metaphysical evolution

00:10:05.290 --> 00:10:09.070 align:middle line:84%
